      * Improve parts in TOC.
      * Clear double page before parts.
    - univie-ling.bbx:
      * Add option "annotations" which, if true, will print out
        the annotation field (useful for annotated bibliographies).
      * Add manual.

V. 2.8 (2024-09-20):
